145
00:12:23,176 --> 00:12:26,716
-Not just to the RBMK,
but the entire industry.
-No, no, no, no, no.

146
00:12:26,801 --> 00:12:29,221
-They can't function
without us.
-No, no, no.

147
00:12:29,301 --> 00:12:31,511
Do you know
what happened to Volkov

148
00:12:31,593 --> 00:12:34,053
