149
00:12:34,134 --> 00:12:38,844
They just removed him from
his position at the Institute.

150
00:12:38,926 --> 00:12:42,046
Sacked for the crime
of knowing.

151
00:12:42,134 --> 00:12:44,434
And you think that
these scientists,

152
